meaning_str.bing:
n. 质量；品质；上乘；优质
adj. 优质的；高质量的；盖帽儿了；棒极了
网络. 性质；素质；特性

优质的；高质量的；盖帽儿了；棒极了

品质；质量；特性；特征；特质；属性；才能；优点；（尤指好的）人品；素质；品德；高品质；高标准；上乘；卓越；优秀；优质；等级

1.en: He said: "With his quality he must play like this every game, and we expect him to. "
1.cn: 凭借他的实力，他必须要每场比赛都有这样的表现，我们期待他也能做到。

2.en: The company maintains quality control and the franchises are close enough to the children to make distribution quick and easy.
2.cn: 企业进行质量控制，特营点与儿童很近，让分配快速易行。

3.en: We sold the PLC to provide up to two years of quality assurance, and passed through a rigorous testing and certification.
3.cn: 我们售出的PLC最长提供两年的质量保证，并且都经过了严格的测试和认证。

0.en: This vinegar added to the quality of the beer.

1.cn: 刚刚做父母的人应该得到高质量，可负担的婴儿保育项目。

2.en: In your lifetime, you will face millions of decisions. The quality of your decisions will determine the quality of your life.
2.cn: 在你的一生中你将面对百万个决定。你决定的质量将影响你的生活质量。

3.en: It still creates these expectations that the quality is going to be worse.
3.cn: 他们仍然会感觉质量会比全价差。

4.en: So you moved to a better neighborhood. You think this will give you a higher quality of life.
4.cn: 所以你搬去更好的社区，你认为生活质量会更高。

5.en: And it's that mission, that devotion to quality, and ideals, and heart...
5.cn: 而做产品可以是看做完成一次使命专注于质量、理念，以及人们的内心...

6.en: So, you know how it's not just family time that matters. It's quality family time.
6.cn: 所以你知道重要的不只是跟家人一起的时间，而是高质量的家人共处时光。

7.en: And so the CDOs that you create are of the highest quality and the highest value. Absolutely. Yep. Absolutely.
7.cn: 所以你发行的债务担保是质量最好价值最高的。绝对的。绝对的。

8.en: President Stenborg, you make it sound like you don't care about the quality of the education. Is that true?
8.cn: 斯滕堡校长，你说的这些让人觉得你好像根本不在乎教育的质量，是这样吗？

9.en: Granted, my methods may have been somewhat unorthodox, but I think the end result will be a measurable enhancement to penny's quality of life.
9.cn: 就算是吧，我的方法可能有点唐突，但是我认为这能很好的提高佩妮的生活质量。

10.en: There's more. The applications go beyond the disease. There are indications that show that therapy can improve cognitive functioning, memory quality.
10.cn: 还有这种药物的作用已经不止于治病，有迹象表明该疗法能改善认知机能和记忆质量。

11.en: But through no one's fault, Penny, the quality of dinner conversation in this apartment has declined. And again, I'm looking at no one in particular, Penny.
11.cn: 虽然没人有错，佩妮，但晚餐谈话的质量的确下滑了。再次重申，这事谁都不怪，佩妮。

12.en: Penny, this is your enterprise, so it's ultimately your decision, but based on the quality of his work, I'd strongly recommend that we let Leonard go.
12.cn: 佩妮，这是你的公司，所以最终决议权在于你，但基于他工作的质量，我强烈建议开除莱纳德。

13.en: Look, These genomes, these 23 chromosomes, they don't in any way represent the quality of our relationships or the nature of our society, at least not yet.
13.cn: 这个，这些基因组，这23个染色体它们并不代表我们人际关系的质量，或者我们这个社会的性质，至少目前还没有。

14.en: Sheldon, that isn't necessary. No, it is. Leonard pointed out to me that I'm not always a loving and supportive boyfriend, so here's some quality luggage. Thank you.
14.cn: 谢尔顿，你不用这么做。不，我需要。莱纳德告诉我我并不是一个时常能给予你爱与支持的男朋友，所以我给你买了高质量的行李箱。谢谢。

15.en: No, not so fast there, OK. You make a quality offer.
15.cn: 别急、别急，你开的条件不错。

16.en: Bert did quality research. And he deserves whatever accolades he receives.
16.cn: 伯特的研究做得不错，他受到表彰也是理所当然的。

17.en: Ava has quality I like. You're kidding me? She's just like my friend Marisol.
17.cn: 艾娃身上有我喜欢的特质。你逗我呢吧？她很像我的朋友玛丽索。

18.en: Manhattan is the best place to buy quality Christmas gifts. We have 40 bucks.
18.cn: 曼哈顿是最适合买好圣诞礼物的地方了，我们有四十块钱。

19.en: Why is it inside out? Excuse me. But this is a purebred, show-quality Sphinx cat.
19.cn: 它的皮怎么翻出来了？帮帮忙，这可是展示级的纯种斯芬克斯猫。
